{"tid":505211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"綠色和平成員 爬中環摩天輪抗議","createTime":"2017-12-21T01:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T07:02:08.000Z","uid":62192,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e8cb8bc2000b115e504a6c6ceb3126cc4751d999","tid":505211,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:10:31.000Z","msg":"早上約7時15分，12名穿著橙色衣服的綠色和平成員，爬上中環摩天輪，準備掛橫額抗議過量使用即棄塑膠。消防高空拯救隊及警方到場戒備。據了解，環保組職綠色和平，今次就快餐連瑣店年派逾4億件即棄塑膠表達不滿，參與行動的5男7女均繫有安全繩。<br />\n<br />\n中環摩天輪停止運作4個月，於昨天早上11時重開。成人門票由過往100元大幅減至20元，吸引不少市民專程到場乘搭。綠色和平發言人指，選擇在摩天輪掛橫額，純粹想多些人見到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171221&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57608137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171221%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57608137&d=Lae4Q969r7wfmezT87%2Byq8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3cbbf9c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171221%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57608137&h=2de96a4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171221&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57608137</a>"},{"pid":"1aceec7f745d04c0b24525d731f2f8b400bc8900","tid":505211,"uid":36820,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"fec9b31a24f6c96e21560918677eef02a4af3147","tid":505211,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"b597484a597fec9d1ff1ad27cbb92d64983b92aa","tid":505211,"uid":14256,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:13:33.000Z","msg":"D橫額用咩做？"},{"pid":"6f6023f44c96f8eac5b40013cfdc72891c8bcd64","tid":505211,"uid":61091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:13:52.000Z","msg":"環保塔利班"},{"pid":"98fff7b722d5d57d80d88a6fcf52163c1f4df678","tid":505211,"uid":58512,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"有無人